Thank you so much for getting back to me, my amazing lawyer Sigrid was able to get me there- due 
to the short notice & long flight I was afraid I was going to miss the hearing, so she got me there... 
impressive!! Thank you so much Sigrid!! 
On the return a that would be great if you could help out with the cost. I can give you my details if 
needed. Also due to an ongoing medical condition, I would need to fly business. It does help me with not 
being stuck in a position for 24+ hours. Thank you so very much!! 
All the 
best,

Thank you.
